Do I want to be
right about this,

00:36:32.360 --> 00:36:35.140
that all men are
untrustworthy, all will women

00:36:35.140 --> 00:36:38.622
are nuts, usually are
the two that come out.

00:36:38.622 --> 00:36:40.080
Or do I want to
break through this,

00:36:40.080 --> 00:36:41.496
because I actually
want something.

00:36:41.496 --> 00:36:43.860
I want to be higher
up that J-curve.

00:36:43.860 --> 00:36:49.410
Here's one of the best named
professors in business, Sydney

00:36:49.410 --> 00:36:52.830
Finkelstein, who did a
