Let them come to you.

00:41:50.630 --> 00:41:53.880
Notice any physical
feelings in your body.

00:41:53.880 --> 00:41:57.090
And then bring this problem
that you want to break through,

00:41:57.090 --> 00:41:59.680
the juicer, it can be a
new one, not even the one

00:41:59.680 --> 00:42:01.170
you've been working on.

00:42:01.170 --> 00:42:02.926
Like if you broke
through this, your life

00:42:02.926 --> 00:42:04.417
would never be the same again.

00:42:04.417 --> 00:42:06.250
Bring that problem into
your mind right now.

00:42:10.720 --> 00:42:13.470
Just notice what you want
to do with it with hands,

00:42:13.470 --> 00:42:15.020
this meaty, juicy problem.

00:42:18.140 --> 00:42:21.278
And then what you say about it.

00:42:21.278 --> 00:42:25.530
And there's usually, those
sayings, usually come down to,

00:42:25.530 --> 00:42:27.462
you're wrong, or
the world's wrong.

00:42:27.462 --> 00:42:29.170
I'm wrong, something
about me, or there's

00:42:29.170 --> 00:42:30.461
something wrong with the world.

00:42:33.030 --> 00:42:35.520
And then, feel the
emotional stuff.

00:42:35.520 --> 00:42:37.900
Feel where you're gut's at,
feel where your lungs are at,

00:42:37.900 --> 00:42:40.860
feel your heart rate.

00:42:40.860 --> 00:42:43.190
Feel whether you want
to breathe big, open,

00:42:43.190 --> 00:42:45.320
or kind of short and tense.

