conscious and
aware of it, I want

00:42:56.320 --> 00:43:00.750
you to imagine all the
human beings right now

00:43:00.750 --> 00:43:03.580
in the world who are dealing
with gnarly problems, problems

00:43:03.580 --> 00:43:09.486
many of them probably more grave
or challenging than our own.

00:43:09.486 --> 00:43:14.940
And think about how many
people coming into the world--

00:43:14.940 --> 00:43:19.530
whether they've been abused
or refugees or all the people,

00:43:19.530 --> 00:43:22.030
suicidal at some
point, but they've

00:43:22.030 --> 00:43:25.650
managed to find a
way to come back

00:43:25.650 --> 00:43:30.790
with creativity and
compassion, with leadership.

00:43:30.790 --> 00:43:34.800
Imagine how many millions of
people there are, like us.

00:43:34.800 --> 00:43:37.310
And imagine how
many millions have

00:43:37.310 --> 00:43:42.150
been able to do this since
the beginning of time--

00:43:42.150 --> 00:43:48.080
to bring something more
back, to expand their heart,

00:43:48.080 --> 00:43:50.530
and to bring more love
and passion and compassion

00:43:50.530 --> 00:43:55.390
and caring with their children,
other people's children.

00:43:55.390 --> 00:44:01.330
We all have access to that
power, to make a difference.

00:44:03.860 --> 00:44:09.020
Just feel them now in
you, and you in them.

00:44:09.020 --> 00:44:12.870
And now notice how your heart
feels about your challenge.

00:44:19.175 --> 00:44:24.190
And now what you say
about it, and the ideas

00:44:24.190 --> 00:44:26.530
that come to mind, why
