00:49:03.090 --> 00:49:06.460
Consciously look at releasing
your own beliefs and habits

00:49:06.460 --> 00:49:09.865
before you break down and
proactively ride this curve.

00:49:09.865 --> 00:49:12.240
Because you're all on a curve
in every hour of your life.

